Name: virtual_network_subnet_ids
Description: The list of Subnet IDs to associate with the File Share. This must be a list of valid Subnet IDs.

Name: ip_rules
Description: The list of IP addresses that are allowed to access the File Share. This must be a list of valid IP addresses.
